c945			; | SPITIME ( -- u1 )   Pushes address of the SPI pulse counter/delay to stack | DONE 
c945			; 
c945			; | | If using BANK devices then leave as is. 
c945			; | | Only really useful for the CARTDEV where other devices may be far too slow. In particular 
